<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-67444-1"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-67444-1')">1</a>. BTW: It seems that Titania is a fae goddess, given the current <a href="http://kaktuskontainer.wikidot.com/djkaktusiii">draft for the demon hector.</a></div>
</div>

